e. New public params use `Annotated[bool, Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")] = Default(True|False)`. Non-public internal `APIRoute.__init__` may use plain `auto_head: bool | DefaultPlaceholder = Default(True)`. Method-order list and helpers live in `fastapi/routing.py`.",
