+Memory~512-1024MB
+CPUUsage%85
+
+[Logic]
+RequireAuth&ValidToken&¬Expired
+UseCache||UseDB
+
+[Attribution]
+©Claude>implemented::Feature
+©User>requested::Change
+
+[Evolution]
+V1→V2→V3{current}
+Simple→Complex→Optimized
+```
